OL,3,CFailure to order Sean Brown public
OL,4,Cinquiry 'unlawful', court rules
OL,6,FThe Government's failure to order a
OL,7,Fpublic inquiry into the murder of GAA
OL,8,Fofficial Sean Brown in 1997 was
OL,9,Funlawful and "cannot stand", the Court
OL,10,Fof Appeal in Belfast has ruled.
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland's Lady Chief Justice
OL,13,FDame Siobhan Keegan said she would not
OL,14,Fmake a mandatory order at this point
OL,15,Fthat Northern Ireland Secretary Hilary
OL,16,FBenn should establish a statutory
OL,17,Finquiry, but has instead given him
OL,18,Ffour weeks to "reflect upon the
OL,19,Fjudgment of the court".
