OL,3,CFailure to order Sean Brown public
OL,4,Cinquiry 'unlawful', court rules
OL,6,FMr Brown, 61, the chairman of Bellaghy
OL,7,FWolfe Tones GAA club in Co
OL,8,FLondonderry, was ambushed, kidnapped
OL,9,Fand murdered by loyalist
OL,10,Fparamilitaries as he locked the gates
OL,11,Fof the club in May 1997.
OL,13,FNo-one has ever been convicted of his
OL,14,Fkilling.
OL,16,FThe Government had appealed against a
OL,17,Fdecision by the High Court last year
OL,18,Fto order a public inquiry to be held
OL,19,Finto the murder.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
