OL,6,FDelivering the judgment on Thursday,
OL,7,Fthe Lady Chief Justice said: "We find
OL,8,Fthe decision to refuse a public
OL,9,Finquiry cannot stand and is unlawful
OL,10,Fand in breach of Article 2
OL,11,Fobligations."
