OL,3,CFailure to order Sean Brown public
OL,4,Cinquiry 'unlawful', court rules
OL,6,FMr Benn decided against holding an
OL,7,Finquiry, arguing that the case could
OL,8,Finstead be dealt with by a new
OL,9,FTroubles investigatory body, the
OL,10,FIndependent Commission for
OL,11,FReconciliation and Information
OL,12,FRecovery.
OL,14,FMr Brown's widow Bridie challenged Mr
OL,15,FBenn's decision not to order a public
OL,16,Finquiry and High Court judge Mr
OL,17,FJustice Humphreys found in her favour
OL,18,Fin December and ordered the Government
OL,19,Fto establish one.
