OL,6,FThe Government then appealed against
OL,7,Fthat decision.
OL,9,FSpeaking outside the Royal Courts of
OL,10,FJustice in Belfast, Mr Brown's widow
OL,11,FBridie urged Northern Ireland
OL,12,FSecretary Hilary Benn "to do the right
OL,13,Fthing" and set up a public inquiry
OL,14,Finto her husband's murder.
OL,16,FIt was the 58th time the 87-year-old
OL,17,Fhad attended a court hearing as part
OL,18,Fof her long battle to secure answers
OL,19,Fabout her husband's death.
