OL,6,FShe said: "Mr Benn, five judges have
OL,7,Ftold you what to do.
OL,9,F"Do the right thing and please don't
OL,10,Fhave me going to London."
OL,12,FMr Brown's daughter, Clare Loughran,
OL,13,Fsupported her mother outside court and
OL,14,Fsaid her family felt very positive
OL,15,Fabout the judgment.
