OL,6,FShe said: "As my mum has said, five
OL,7,Fjudges have now told us that really
OL,8,Fthe only way to have a truthful and
OL,9,Fhonest investigation of my father's
OL,10,Fdeath has been an inquiry... we're
OL,11,Fvery pleased with the judgment so far
OL,12,Ftoday.
OL,14,F"Five judges have told him (Mr Benn)
OL,15,Fwhat to do.
