OL,6,F"I think at this stage now he has got
OL,7,Fvery little further option, the fact
OL,8,Fthat he was trying to get us to go
OL,9,Ftowards the ICRIR, and it's been
OL,10,Fevident now today that that is
OL,11,Fprobably something that is not
OL,12,Fappropriate in my father's case,
OL,13,Fcertainly not as it stands at the
OL,14,Fminute."
OL,16,FShe added that she feels the
OL,17,FGovernment has "tried to draw this out
OL,18,Ffor 28 years".
