OL,6,FShe said: "We have had numerous
OL,7,Fsecretary of states come through the
OL,8,Fnorth since my father was murdered,
OL,9,Fand very little of them to date have
OL,10,Fgiven us any sort of hope or very
OL,11,Flittle trust in them.
OL,13,F"At this stage now, we really feel
OL,14,Fthat if they can do the right thing by
OL,15,Four side, we would be delighted with
OL,16,Fthat."
OL,18,FShe said they would like to see a
OL,19,Fpublic inquiry into her father's death
OL,20,Fget under way as soon as possible.
